rible. I told him that I had just seen a group of art advisors from Hong Ko=
ng in line at the =E2=80=9CHong Kong Cafe.=E2=80=9D<br/><br/>I really wante=
d to spend some time talking about the Tom Wesselmann retrospective at the =
Fondation Louis Vuitton. But there was too much to shoehorn into this newsl=
etter. I may take some space on Tuesday to discuss that show in relation to=
 Wesselmann=E2=80=99s market. It=E2=80=99s interesting. <br/><br/>More to t=
he point, the quality of the shows at the Cartier Foundation, Fondation LV,=
